---
import Projects from "./Projects.astro";
import SemiFooter from "./SemiFooter.astro";


---


<section class="pt-12 flex flex-col gap-24 md:gap-44">
    
    <article class=" max-w-2xl flex flex-col justify-center items-center sm:items-start gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl text-balance !leading-[5.5rem]">Independent Software Designer.</h2>

        <ul class="[&_h6]:transition-colors [&_h6]:duration-300 [&_h6]:cursor-pointer [&_h6]:text-[#8a847a] hover:[&_h6]:text-white flex flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4">
            <li>
                <h6 class="initTitle-1 !text-white">For anyone</h6></li>
            <li>
                <h6 class="initTitle-2">Web</h6></li>
            <li>
                <h6 class="initTitle-3">Product</h6></li>
            <li>
                <h6 class="initTitle-4">Advisory</h6></li>
        </ul>

        <ul class="flex flex-row [&_p]:opacity-0 [&_p]:transition-opacity [&_p]:duration-500">
            <li>
                <p class="initText-1 !opacity-100">I design and build software with the goal of telling stories, reducing friction, and crafting digital experiences that are a joy to use.</p></li>
            <li>
                <p class="initText-2 hidden">I pair my background of technical and visual skills plus experience working with no-code tools to deliver websites that perform and convert.</p></li>
            <li>
                <p class="initText-3 hidden">From wire framing to building design systems and high fidelity prototypes, I design products with your customers’ experience in mind. I’ll work closely with your engineers to ensure a consistent high quality product is shipped.</p></li>
            <li>
                <p class="initText-4 hidden">From strategy and positioning, to fractional leadership, I work closely with founders to solve complex problems, and help them define and chart their company’s future.</p></li>
        </ul>
    </article>

    <Projects />

    <SemiFooter />
</section>